'''HCL AppScan'''（原'''IBM Security AppScan'''）是原[[IBM|IBM]]的{{tsl|en|Rational Software|Rational软件}}部门的一组网络安全测试和监控工具，2019年被[[HCL技術|HCL技術]]公司收購。AppScan旨在在开发过程中对Web应用程序的安全漏洞进行测试<ref>开发阶段是解决此类问题的成本最低的阶段。</ref>。该产品学习每个应用程序的行为，无论是现成的或是内部开发的应用程序；该产品还开发了一个程序，用来测试应用程序所有功能的常见的和特定的安全漏洞。

==历史==
AppScan最初是由[[以色列|以色列]]软件公司Sanctum Ltd.（其最初命名为Perfecto Technologies）开发的，1998年首次发布。<ref>{{cite news|title=Perfecto Technologies Becomes Sanctum, Inc.; Pioneerin Automated Web Application Control and Security Changes Name.|url=http://www.allbusiness.com/technology/software-services-applications-internet-social/6459219-1.html#ixzz1dLGMEQ5p|newspaper=BusinessWire|date=2000-06-21}}</ref>1999年Sanctum扩展了其网络安全解决方案，并推出了世界上第一个应用防火墙——AppShield。<ref>{{cite news|title=New tool blocks wily e-comm hacker tricks|url=http://www.cnn.com/TECH/computing/9909/07/ecomm.hack.idg/index.html|author=Ellen Messmer|date=1999-09-07|accessdate=2010-11-17|publisher=CNN|archive-date=2010-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100529111033/http://www.cnn.com/TECH/computing/9909/07/ecomm.hack.idg/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

AppScan的第2版发布于2001年2月，增加了策略识别引擎和[[知识库|知识库]]，自动及自定义的[[網路蜘蛛|爬虫]]引擎和攻击模拟器。<ref>{{cite news|last=Mimoso|first=Michael S.|title=AppScan release secures Web applications|url=http://searchsecurity.techtarget.com/news/520223/Quick-Takes-AppScan-release-secures-Web-applications|newspaper=SearchSecurity|date=2001-02-06|access-date=2014-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140912024734/http://searchsecurity.techtarget.com/news/520223/Quick-Takes-AppScan-release-secures-Web-applications|archive-date=2014-09-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>第3版发布于2002年4月，增加了协同测试功能——不同的任务可以分配给不同的测试者；改进了程序的扫描和报表部分的用户界面。<ref>{{cite news|last=Costello|first=Sam|title=Sanctum boosts tests, reports in AppScan 3.0|url=http://www.computerworld.com.au/article/23334/sanctum_boosts_tests_reports_appscan_3_0/|newspaper=Computerworld|date=2002-04-30|accessdate=2014-08-12|archive-date=2014-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140912021706/http://www.computerworld.com.au/article/23334/sanctum_boosts_tests_reports_appscan_3_0/|dead-url=no}}</ref>到2003年，超过500家企业客户使用AppScan，营收达到了3000万美元。<ref name=Jpost>{{cite news |title=Sanctum acquired by Watchfire |url=http://www.ivc-online.com/ivcWeeklyItem.asp?articleID=2015 |newspaper=Israel Venture Capital Research Center |date=2004-07-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20070810083415/http://www.ivc-online.com/ivcWeeklyItem.asp?articleID=2015 |archivedate=2007-08-10 |accessdate=2014-08-12 }}</ref>

2004年7月，[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]的公司{{tsl|en|Watchfire}}收购了Sanctum，这是一家开发了名为WebXM的Web应用管理平台的公司。AppScan成为了Watchfire公司的主打产品，以色列[[赫兹利亚|赫兹利亚]]的Sanctum研发中心则成为Watchfire公司的主要研发地。<ref name=Jpost />

2007年6月，Watchfire公司被IBM收购，并纳入{{tsl|en|Rational Software|Rational软件}}产品线，使IBM能够覆盖更多的应用程序开发生命周期。<ref>{{cite news|last=Ogren|first=Eric|title=AppScan lives on with IBM|url=http://blogs.computerworld.com/node/5652|newspaper=Computerworld|date=2007-06-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110131081131/http://blogs.computerworld.com/node/5652|archivedate=2011-01-31|accessdate=2014-08-12}}</ref>Watchfire公司的研发中心被并入IBM在以色列的研发实验室。<ref>{{cite news|title=Watchfire Israel goes to IBM|url=http://www.globes.co.il/serveen/globes/docview.asp?did=1000219398|newspaper=Globes|date=2007-06-07}}</ref>

2009年，IBM收购了{{tsl|en|Ounce Labs}}，为AppScan产品线增加了一个在开发过程中查找和纠正源代码中漏洞的工具，并改名为AppScan Source Edition。<ref>{{cite news|last=Rick|first=Whiting|title=IBM: Design Security Into New Applications During Development|url=http://www.crn.com/news/security/225500021/ibm-design-security-into-new-applications-during-development.htm;jsessionid=sAdQrMEqh7kWNepNsBEm-w**.ecappj02|newspaper=CRN|date=2010-06-08|accessdate=2014-08-12|archive-date=2014-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140912030836/http://www.crn.com/news/security/225500021/ibm-design-security-into-new-applications-during-development.htm;jsessionid=sAdQrMEqh7kWNepNsBEm-w**.ecappj02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年，IBM將AppScan賣給了印度的[[HCL技術|HCL技術]]公司。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Campbell Kwan |title=HCL now fully controls IBM software including Notes and Domino |url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/hcl-now-fully-controls-ibm-software-including-notes-and-domino/ |website=ZDNet |publisher=CBS Interactive |accessdate=2020-08-31 |date=2019-07-02 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801190637/https://www.zdnet.com/article/hcl-now-fully-controls-ibm-software-including-notes-and-domino/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

